videos.description: West Virginia hits a big 3-pointer, steals the inbounds pass and immediately hits another big three.
videos.headline: WVU hits two 3s in 10 seconds

videos.description: Chase Harler goes full swat team when Davonta Jordan goes for the layup.
videos.headline: Harler comes up with monster block

videos.description: CJ Massinburg drains a big 3-pointer to get Buffalo within two vs. West Virginia late in the second half.
videos.headline: Buffalo hits big 3 to get back in game

videos.description: CJ Massinburg hits a 3-pointer to tie the game at 84-84 for Buffalo in the final minute.
videos.headline: Buffalo ties up West Virginia with 14 seconds left
